titles: Mobile Mix: EE scores 5G winner at Wembley
data: We’re at Wembley Stadium in London this week, as EE went on the 5G attack by holding a live demo between the venue and Huawei’s Global Mobile Broadband Forum (MBBF), which took place across the city. Kavit was on hand at MBBF to report the event’s highlights, while Chris rounds up the biggest news.
